533
00:43:43,525 --> 00:43:45,459
Thank you for your understanding.

534
00:43:47,059 --> 00:43:49,925
- Then, please take care of it. 
 - Yes.

535
00:43:50,525 --> 00:43:52,625
I will take my leave first.

536
00:43:57,092 --> 00:43:58,925
Please go ahead.

537
00:44:00,992 --> 00:44:03,492
I'll take measurements while waiting.

