677
00:52:55,125 --> 00:52:58,359
It resembles a cheap, countryside motel!

678
00:52:58,359 --> 00:52:59,725
Take a closer look.

679
00:52:59,725 --> 00:53:02,059
This design is subpar.

680
00:53:02,059 --> 00:53:07,792
Ji Kang Hee, whom you brought in, is nothing more than a subpar girl from the countryside.

681
00:53:13,525 --> 00:53:16,825
If I'm subpar, you can't be more than filth, Mr. Mok.

682
00:53:16,825 --> 00:53:19,759
- Obsolete, just patching together other people's designs. 
 - What?

683
00:53:19,759 --> 00:53:23,292
Copying and pasting anything that looks good from all sorts of archives.

684
00:53:23,292 --> 00:53:25,625
Abusing your authority to take credit for thumbnails created by your team members.

685
00:53:25,625 --> 00:53:28,092
- No, that's malicious. 
 - You… Are you done talking?

686
00:53:28,092 --> 00:53:31,425
While you're at it, take my stuff too.

687
00:53:31,425 --> 00:53:33,325
Enough!

688
00:53:33,325 --> 00:53:34,859
Take it and get out.

689
00:53:34,859 --> 00:53:37,325
- You're fired! 
 - No!

690
00:53:37,325 --> 00:53:38,959
It's you who should be fired.

691
00:53:38,959 --> 00:53:41,892
Completely out of my life!

692
00:53:47,292 --> 00:53:48,892
Out!

693
00:53:56,625 --> 00:53:59,859
   

694
00:53:59,859 --> 00:54:02,692
 I'm sorry for the opportunity you gave me. 

695
00:54:02,692 --> 00:54:05,192
 It's not Kang Hee's fault, I'll somehow… 

696
00:54:05,192 --> 00:54:06,759
 No. 

697
00:54:06,759 --> 00:54:10,792
 It's more comfortable and honorable to sweat at a construction site. 

698
00:54:11,892 --> 00:54:14,225
 I will stop here. 

699
00:55:10,592 --> 00:55:14,859
 I didn't come to Seoul to live like this. 

700
00:55:21,125 --> 00:55:25,559
 I didn't abandon you to live such a lousy life. 

701
00:56:33,125 --> 00:56:37,225
 Did you know? Family members can't get married. 

702
00:56:37,225 --> 00:56:40,025
 Why get married when we're already family? 

703
00:56:40,825 --> 00:56:44,659
 No. I'm going marry you.  

704
00:56:44,659 --> 00:56:48,659
 Marry me, Kang Hee. 

705
00:56:48,659 --> 00:56:50,859
 What are you saying? 

706
00:56:50,859 --> 00:56:54,359
 Huh? It's snowing. 

