744
01:00:56,025 --> 01:00:58,259
Kang Hee should come, too.

745
01:00:58,259 --> 01:01:01,092
You think she'd come? She's been out of touch for 10 years.

746
01:01:01,092 --> 01:01:04,192
She has to. She's practically his granddaughter.

747
01:01:04,192 --> 01:01:06,892
Grandfather loved her so much.

748
01:01:06,892 --> 01:01:12,059
I heard Ahjusshi contacted her, but there was no response.

749
01:01:12,059 --> 01:01:14,025
That Ji Kang Hee, seriously…

750
01:01:14,025 --> 01:01:15,860
If she really doesn't show up this time,

751
01:01:15,860 --> 01:01:17,350
I'm going to cut ties with her.

752
01:01:17,359 --> 01:01:21,592
Honestly, I hope she doesn't come.

753
01:01:24,192 --> 01:01:25,970
Yeon Soo is just starting to live well.

754
01:01:25,970 --> 01:01:28,992
If Kang Hee comes and shakes things up again…

755
01:01:28,992 --> 01:01:32,225
What can we do, that poor kid?

756
01:01:40,992 --> 01:01:42,459
I'll have a drink for him.

757
01:01:42,459 --> 01:01:45,125
Hey, easy. I can't hold much liquor.

758
01:01:45,125 --> 01:01:47,192
Oh, that's enough.

759
01:01:47,192 --> 01:01:50,825
He was bedridden for a long time, wasn't he?

760
01:01:50,825 --> 01:01:52,492
- That's right. 
 - Yes, that's right.

761
01:01:52,492 --> 01:01:55,992
They say Yeon Soo didn't even cry.

762
01:01:55,992 --> 01:01:57,530
He must be in shock, you know.

763
01:01:57,530 --> 01:01:59,490
