764
01:01:59,492 --> 01:02:02,359
Why did Soon Ja choose to get married now, of all times?

765
01:02:02,359 --> 01:02:04,559
It's not Soon Ja, it's Su Ji!

766
01:02:04,559 --> 01:02:06,125
And what do you mean, "of all times"?

767
01:02:06,125 --> 01:02:08,325
Should she have pushed back her marriage just because her father is bedridden?

768
01:02:08,325 --> 01:02:11,059
Chun Pil taking the role of the chief mourner is enough. What's the issue?

769
01:02:11,059 --> 01:02:13,792
But Chun Pil must have contacted Kang Hee, right?

770
01:02:13,792 --> 01:02:15,692
- He must have. 
 - Anyway,

771
01:02:15,692 --> 01:02:19,192
I wonder how Kang Hee has changed.

772
01:02:19,192 --> 01:02:20,825
You think that temper of hers would've left her?

773
01:02:20,825 --> 01:02:24,025
