774
01:02:24,025 --> 01:02:26,492
Ah, right, Gang Hee.

775
01:02:26,492 --> 01:02:27,825
Hey! Hey! Hey!

776
01:02:27,825 --> 01:02:30,292
- Ji Kang Hee is here. Ji Kang Hee. 
 - Hey, Ji Kang Hee! Ji Kang Hee!

777
01:02:30,292 --> 01:02:31,825
Hey, Ji Kang Hee is here! Ji Kang Hee!

778
01:02:31,825 --> 01:02:33,792
- What? 
 - Kang Hee is here!

779
01:02:33,792 --> 01:02:35,459
- What are you talking about? 
